# JARVIS 3.0 – Your Personal AI Assistant 🤖  
Built by **Shaan / SHAANX STUDIOS**

![Jarvis Banner](banner.png)

Jarvis 3.0 is a Python-based AI assistant with support for:
- 💬 Chat (GPT-4)
- 🧠 Knowledge Q&A
- 📄 Generate PDF / DOCX / PPTX
- 🎨 Image Generation via OpenAI DALL·E
- 🗣️ Voice control (in advanced versions)

## 🛠️ Features

- `who created you`: Replies with creator name
- `pdf: <text>`: Creates a PDF
- `docx: <text>`: Creates a Word doc
- `ppt: <text>`: Makes a PowerPoint
- `image: <prompt>`: Generates an image using AI
- General GPT-4 Q&A support

## ⚙️ How to Run

### 1. Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/jarvis-ai.git
cd jarvis-ai
